Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident is the greatest scandal\Nin the history of the Czech Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Regrettably, the three murdered men
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,had connections with\Nthe former Czechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,these murders have wiped out\Nall unsavory ties to the Prague station.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all officers\Nof this proud Czech Police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you all to act honorably.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As the new commissioner,\NI will work to regain people's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will implement thorough reforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce the five members
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of the special task force\Nsent here from the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to cooperate with them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so these atrocious crimes can be solved\Nas quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Suk, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As the new commissioner,\NI'd like to express my appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for your work on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally,\Nwhat case are you working on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The case Inspector Zeman\Nwas working on, the murder of Petrov,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the man running the unlicensed orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue working on your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. There's one other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About that tall man who's a suspect\Nin the murder of Inspector Zeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have you found out anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I haven't found anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You may go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Jan Suk."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Assigned to Prague Station a year ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Had a close relationship with\NInspector Zeman since he started."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Exposed the hidden past of both\Ndetectives Patera and Janáček."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Met with Commissioner Hamrlík\Njust before his death."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keep an eye on that man.\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was pretty happy\Nwhen you answered the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at the hotel\Nthat you said you were staying at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think\Nyou have been betrayed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer, you said\Nwe should meet in a crowded place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The new commissioner still suspects you\Nin the murder of Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Czechoslovakia secret police\Nare still after you too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Or maybe somewhere crowded\Nis a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-There are no safe places.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone wants to get me,\Nthey can do it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, they could do it\Nfrom that window with red curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer, who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a struggling journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Then why are\Nthese things happening to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because\NI stuck my nose in too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to laugh about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They tried to take your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't mind.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this might happen\Nwhen I snooped around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Presently, Suk is\Nat a cafe in Republic Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we suspected,\Nhe's meeting that tall man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Grimmer for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Should I just keep him\Nunder surveillance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So it happened when you were\Ninvestigating Petrov
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,who had conducted brainwashing experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,on children in former East Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just before Petrov died,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,he gave you that key\Nto a safe deposit box?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He also mentioned\Nthe "origin of the monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Origin of the monster"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it means,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but a lot of people\Nseem to want to get their hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The former secret police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And a blonde-haired woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The children from the orphanage\Nalso told me that after Petrov was killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,they saw a beautiful\Nblonde-haired woman leave the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who that might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got the faintest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you all right?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hiding the fact that you're meeting\Nwith me from your superiors, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay with betraying the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exercising investigatory discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After investigating thoroughly,\NI'll report everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to prove your innocence\Nafter a proper investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly look to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The man reading a paper under\Na parasol to your left looks suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's from the secret police?\N-He could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to the safe deposit box\Nthat I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know\Nthe truth about this "monster"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you may be better off not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking pretty pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I must be imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk's on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Suk from the Prague Police.\NI called earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The safe deposit boxes are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You may use that room\Nto examine the contents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Research papers and a cassette tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a tape recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready? I'll play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the voice of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is… Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your last name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your last name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is… Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, in a land far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,there lived a nameless monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster was dying to have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that some kind of story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for Anna…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,while reading a picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy was drugged\Nbefore he was questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a very gifted child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you're afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you most afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask a different question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever killed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like…\Nit was just Anna and me in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the other question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you most afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster inside me\Nis getting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Munch-munch, chomp-chomp,\Ngobble-gobble, gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Munch-munch, chomp-chomp,\Ngobble-gobble, gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Munch-munch, chomp-chomp,\Ngobble-gobble, gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing I am afraid of the most…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling sick! I'm going to throw up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that who the monster is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are still people who want it\Nmore than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the former\NCzechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter whether we listen\Nto some of it or all of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no going back for us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do with that tape\Nand those reports?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them back in the safe deposit box?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Ordinarily,\NI'd leave them here as evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should leave separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it's me\Nthat they're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Tell me your phone number\Nand home address.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we make it back safely,\Nlet's contact each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it home okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a lot of confidence in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,His place is on Lanover Street, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we would like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who we are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're members of\Nthe special task force from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Detective Third Grade Novak\Nand I'm Detective Third Grade Zander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been meeting Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't tell us you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You met him earlier at a cafe\Nin Republic Square
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and then went to Prochazka Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the man\Nin this picture, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Captain Karel Ranke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a big shot in the Czechoslovakia\Nsecret police who went underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We checked your bank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a large deposit this month.\NWhat's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI don't know about any deposit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is hospitalized
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Krumlov National Hospital\Nwith a serious illness, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It must cost a bundle\Njust to cover hospital expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After your mother divorced your father,\Nshe raised you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very close to your mother,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to search your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, look all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hiding anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zander, come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They were in a cabinet in your bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen these before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tell what the drug is\Nuntil It's been tested at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But the muscle relaxant that killed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the three men at the station was found in…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,whiskey bonbons they ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Question me all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but could I change my shirt before I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I explain everything,\Nthey'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell gunpowder smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk!
